r deeds)","transliteration":"liyuraw","root":"رأي","lemmaId":null},{"id":"99:6:6","ayahNum":6,"wordNum":6,"word":"أَعْمٰلَهُمْ","meaning":"their deeds (object of لِّيُرَوْا۟ - so they may see)","transliteration":"aʿmālahum","root":"عمل","lemmaId":2592},{"id":"99:7:1","ayahNum":7,"wordNum":1,"word":"فَمَن","meaning":"then whoever (subject of يَعْمَلْ)","transliteration":"faman","root":"","lemmaId":3464},{"id":"99:7:2","ayahNum":7,"wordNum":2,"word":"يَعْمَلْ","meaning":"he does/will do (in response to فَمَن - so whoever)","transliteration":"yaʿmal","root":"عمل","lemmaId":2592},{"id":"99:7:3","ayahNum":7,"wordNum":3,"word":"مِثْقَالَ","meaning":"a measure of weight (object being measured)","transliteration":"mith'qāla","root":"ثقل","lemmaId":null},{"id":"99:7:4","ayahNum":7,"wordNum":4,"word":"ذَرَّةٍ","meaning":"a tiny particle (weight of مِثْقَالَ)","transliteration":"dharratin","root":"ذرر","lemmaId":null},{"id":"99:7:5","ayahNum":7,"wordNum":5,"word":"خَيْرًا","meaning":"good (as the object being done)","transliteration":"khayran","root":"خير","lemmaId":null},{"id":"99:7:6","ayahNum":7,"wordNum":6,"word":"يَرَهُۥ","meaning":"he will see it (referring to مِثْقَالَ ذَرَّةٍ)","transliteration":"yarahu","root":"رأي","lemmaId":null},{"id":"99:8:1","ayahNum":8,"wordNum":1,"word":"وَمَن","meaning":"and whoever (subject of يَعْمَلْ)","transliteration":"waman","root":"","lemmaId":3464},{"id":"99:8:2","ayahNum":8,"wordNum":2,"word":"يَعْمَلْ","meaning":"he does/will do (jussive mood because it follows مَن)","transliteration":"yaʿmal","root":"عمل","lemmaId":2592},{"id":"99:8:3","ayahNum":8,"wordNum":3,"word":"مِثْقَالَ","meaning":"a measure of weight (object being measured)","transliteration":"mith'qāla","root":"ثقل","lemmaId":null},{"id":"99:8:4","ayahNum":8,"wordNum":4,"word":"ذَرَّةٍ","meaning":"a tiny particle (object of مِثْقَالَ)","transliteration":"dharratin","root":"ذرر","lemmaId":null},{"id":"99:8:5","ayahNum":8,"wordNum":5,"word":"شَرًّا","meaning":"evil (as the object being done)","transliteration":"sharran","root":"شرر","lemmaId":null},{"id":"99:8:6","ayahNum":8,"wordNum":6,"word":"يَرَهُۥ","meaning":"he will see it (referring to the tiny deed mentioned before)","transliteration":"yarahu","root":"رأي","lemmaId":null}]